    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The board of public works has\naddressed a letter to the Washing.\nton Water Power company i'm\npressing on the company the need\nfor the exercise of the utmost care\nconcerning the Sprague avenue\ntrestle while the work of making\nthe fill is in progress. If the con-\ntractors do not keep the trestle in\nsafe condition the city engineer\nwill have the work done at the ex-\npense of the contractors."
